cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the security and privacy aspects of smartphone applications, specifically the permission system in Android. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves a field study with human participants, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Additionally, the paper involves data collection and analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper deals with privacy concerns, which could also place it under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
